âœ… Steps to Install Google Chrome on Ubuntu (With GUI)
1. Open Terminal

You can press Ctrl + Alt + T or open it from your app menu.

2. Download the Google Chrome .deb Package

Command: wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
Command: sudo apt update -y
Command: sudo apt install -y ./google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
Command: google-chrome --version
Command: google-chrome

